  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243540.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>意大利法拉利公司（Ferrari）董事长蒙特泽莫罗（Luca Cordero di Montezemolo）表示，员工应少发电子邮件给同事，如果问题要沟通，最好直接当面说。他认为这种方式虽然老派，“但非常有效” 。</strong>现年65岁的蒙特泽莫罗其实并不排斥新科技，他非常喜欢智能手机和平板电脑。法拉利公司也很擅长利用网络，其在线商店今年第一季度的业绩增长了 25%，并在Facebook上拥有1200万粉丝，在YouTube上的点击率也高达3000万次。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e391cd9/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243540.htm&amp;t=%E6%B3%95%E6%8B%89%E5%88%A9%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E5%B0%91%E5%8F%91%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6+%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243540.htm&amp;t=%E6%B3%95%E6%8B%89%E5%88%A9%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E5%B0%91%E5%8F%91%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6+%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243540.htm&amp;t=%E6%B3%95%E6%8B%89%E5%88%A9%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E5%B0%91%E5%8F%91%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6+%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243540.htm&amp;t=%E6%B3%95%E6%8B%89%E5%88%A9%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E5%B0%91%E5%8F%91%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6+%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96\" target=\