  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243537.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>周五，三星将公布季度利润，尽管Galaxy系列产品开始褪色，新竞争对手夺走市场份额，三星的季度运营利润预期仍将破纪录，达89亿美元。</strong>2012年，拜Galaxy S手机所赐，三星已经超过苹果成为第一大手机商。三星已经连续5个季度利润创新高，直到2013年一季度，现在三星面临的问题是：随着竞争对手潮水般涌入，推出低价、更简洁的智能手机，三星如何保持利润率不下降。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e391cd6/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243537.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E4%BA%8C%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E5%88%A9%E6%B6%A6%E6%88%96%E8%BE%BE89%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E5%86%8D%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243537.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E4%BA%8C%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E5%88%A9%E6%B6%A6%E6%88%96%E8%BE%BE89%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E5%86%8D%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243537.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E4%BA%8C%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E5%88%A9%E6%B6%A6%E6%88%96%E8%BE%BE89%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E5%86%8D%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243537.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E4%BA%8C%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E8%BF%90%E8%90%A5%E5%88%A9%E6%B6%A6%E6%88%96%E8%BE%BE89%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83+%E5%86%8D%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/